ss reports</p>\r\n', 'Primary', '0'), ('562', '45', '8464', 'Status of regulations outlining criteria for recruitment, training and promotion of security actors', 'Status of', '<p>If the Action will support the development of laws/regulations outlining criteria for recruitment, training and promotion of security actors, this is an appropriate output-level indicator.</p>\r\n', '<p>Legislation/policies developed/updated with the support of the Action</p>\r\n', 'Primary', '0'), ('563', '45', '8464', 'Number of human resources and management staff in the security sector trained by the Action on standards/processes relating to recruitment, training and promotion (disaggregated by sex)', 'Number of ', '<p>The more specific you can be about the training topics and target participants in the local context - the better.</p>\r\n', '<p>Database of training participants, disaggregated by sex&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Primary', '0'), ('564', '45', '8465', 'Number of border management/police officials trained by the Action on Integrated Border Management rules, regulations, structures and processes (disaggregated by sex)', 'Number of', '<p>The more specific you can be about the training topics and target participants in the local context - the better.</p>\r\n', '<p>Database of training participants, disaggregated by sex&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Primary', '0'), ('794', '45', '8465', 'Number of police officers trained by the Action on skills related to their duties [please specify topic] (disaggregated by sex)', 'Number of', '<p>The more specific you can be about the training topics and target participants in the local context - the better.</p>\r\n', '<p>Database of training participants, disaggregated by sex&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'Primary', '0'), ('567', '45', '8465', 'Number of pentitentiary staff trained by the Action on response protocols for different types of emergency situations/protection of minors (or another topic)', 'Number of', '<p>The more specific you can be about the training topics and ta